  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to compare the effectiveness in treatment of chronic blepharitis
      either with a phospholipid liposome suspension compared to a conventional therapy
      recommendation using diluted baby shampoo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
